  "texts": [
    "(1) What is an English course syllabus based on IDC via a blending setting at a Chinese college?",
    "(2) Can an IDC course implemented in a blended learning setting effectively enhance the listening and speaking proficiency of Chinese college students?",
    "(3) Can an IDC intervention in a blended learning setting effectively enhance the listening and speaking proficiency of Chinese college students compared to traditional teaching methods?",
    "The strength of IDC lies in promoting student autonomy (Li & Liu, 2022).",
    "In this research, the focus is on establishing the IDC within the context of ESL/EFL classrooms, with a particular emphasis on the longitudinal development of learning interest toward habitual behaviour."
